# Stage 3 Glass Stage card

When editing or shipping **Stage 3 / Pip’s Picks** card UI on Discover:

1. Read and follow **`web/docs/ui/STAGE3_GLASS_STAGE_CARD.md`** (canonical template).
2. Match the golden sample: **`web/docs/ui/artifacts/stage3-glass-stage-card.reference.html`**.
3. **Required:** “Why Pip picked this” is a **closed-by-default drawer** (addictive tap), not a static always-open verdict box.
4. Robin: upright **44px top-right** only — no tilt, no mid-card hero.
5. Dark spatial track + frosted glass + per-pick accent orbs; Ember palette only (no purple SaaS).
6. Browse offers → Google Shopping (never one retailer).

Ingest / full production wiring: use prompt  
`agent-tools/prompts/ingest-stage3-glass-stage-into-discover.md`.
